Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某天。。。我突然被人软禁了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.87,0:00:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此我开始过着无论何时何地都得乖乖听话的生活.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.75,0:00:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了家务事之后我乖乖的等着姐姐过来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.43,0:00:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.44,0:01:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有乖乖等我么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美味的样子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.94,0:01:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你有乖乖忍住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有忍住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.82,0:01:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有射过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.50,0:01:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我答应你射精之前绝对不准射精哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.94,0:01:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勃起也不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勃起也一样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样站起来可不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点勃起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像有点变大的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会遵守约定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天吃这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做这个的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿衣服是不是感觉很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.56,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.66,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这、这个 、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准有感觉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.28,0:02:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.55,0:03:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋看起来很美味的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.61,0:03:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准勃起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.94,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行、不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.43,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像开始变硬了唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你勃起的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会变得更痛而已欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好要忍住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.71,0:04:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这边好像变大了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痛吧，不可以勃起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以破坏约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然蛋蛋会受伤哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋蛋会受伤哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦的人可是你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵守约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然吃苦的可是蛋蛋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样摸、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样摸不行么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准勃起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要遵守约定才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.86,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我也会不遵守约定哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想办法忍住哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人愉快的早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得出门上班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也要乖乖的看家哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经快一个月了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你能够忍耐一个月的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候我会好好奖赏你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要忍住哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.88,0:06:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的姐姐叫 冲田 杏梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.11,0:07:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射精管理姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对、对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问的不是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的内裤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起、一不小心就、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忍不住么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.55,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我、我已经忍二十七天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经二十七天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只差那么几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看待这种东西。。。。要我怎么。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站到那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢破坏约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股被看光了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起、我不该自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁眼没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在动哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想自慰么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不做我真的会疯掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.52,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗？是这里要疯掉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.97,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的这么想我拆下来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我拆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就稍稍拆下来一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你都忍了二十七天了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有今天而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我憋的好痛苦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哎、、、看起来有点、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直朝着这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快帮我拆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我拆掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？蛋蛋快爆炸了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要爆炸了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.74,0:12:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边和这边都肿起来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.95,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就特别准你、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.86,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的品尝久违的解放感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起、、、被打屁股让我射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打屁股让你射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他射的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.99,0:13:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害，这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.44,0:13:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直忍耐、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大份的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都还没做哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想自慰吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.58,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会帮你做  你自己自慰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.47,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光这样我觉得有点无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆出刚刚的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翘高点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握住你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样自慰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这么丢人的姿势自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变的更硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是变态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我玩腻这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换个姿势吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.62,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看清楚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得很清楚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.31,0:16:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很像自慰嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让肉棒变得更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.66,0:16:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在变得更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更硬吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它变得硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.78,0:16:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它变得更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙、这样不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.10,0:17:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿哒哒的，真是可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在更兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了、要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有三天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩的好开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你、我玩得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再忍三天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你敢射的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就一年...不，两年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，，，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年不让你射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.55,0:18:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要在戴回去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说，还剩下三天哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住，忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.36,0:18:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你软了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你软了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得把它戴回去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这个放这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变得这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是“对不起我勃起了”才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我勃起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.22,0:20:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒变得这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样要我怎么出去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要忍住哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汁流出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以射么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得我们的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.19,0:22:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不准射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.77,0:22:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起没我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.44,0:22:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.41,0:22:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.08,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准射出来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我缩回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.29,0:23:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让精液流回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.83,0:23:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你还是听不懂嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.63,0:23:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的肉棒变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在赶时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.05,0:23:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.26,0:23:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没时间再陪你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.97,0:23:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点让肉棒变小才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在赶时间哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.91,0:23:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.92,0:24:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.51,0:24:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒硬邦邦了哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.32,0:24:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在胸部里变得更硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.19,0:24:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.03,0:24:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.76,0:24:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要忍住哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.23,0:25:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这根下流又肮脏的肉棒 现在可是被我的胸部夹住了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.61,0:25:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点变小哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.98,0:25:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我会兴奋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.02,0:25:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会害我浪费更多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.96,0:25:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒！我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.23,0:25:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让肉棒变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.05,0:25:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先这样弄这里反应很厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.99,0:25:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒又变得更硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.80,0:26:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！我有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.80,0:26:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有感觉么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.54,0:26:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.17,0:26:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要变小才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.05,0:26:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准射出来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.73,0:26:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让你的肉棒变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.67,0:26:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.64,0:26:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.21,0:26:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是没用哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.38,0:26:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是废物，请让我射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.52,0:26:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能让你射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.82,0:26:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快变小啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.03,0:27:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不准射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.81,0:27:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.11,0:27:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.69,0:27:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点变小哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.67,0:27:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变得更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.74,0:27:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.45,0:27:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.28,0:28:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒变得更硬了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.05,0:28:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点想办法变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.11,0:28:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.08,0:28:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要变硬是变小才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.31,0:28:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.85,0:29:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.42,0:29:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.43,0:29:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你就是不听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.17,0:29:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说不准变大么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.34,0:29:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是变大的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.72,0:29:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己不会扭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.30,0:29:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.37,0:30:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒不停的插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.48,0:30:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.78,0:30:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点变小吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.62,0:30:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腰怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.69,0:30:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，腰停不下牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.23,0:30:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是要你变硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.57,0:30:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.37,0:30:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.14,0:30:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是不变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.25,0:30:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让它变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.05,0:30:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是要他变大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.13,0:31:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.51,0:31:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.22,0:31:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.39,0:31:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我控制不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.42,0:31:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让它变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.63,0:31:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不能射么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.10,0:31:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.18,0:31:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抖得好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.02,0:31:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.42,0:31:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.89,0:32:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.10,0:32:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.97,0:32:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应为我太笨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.17,0:32:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.85,0:32:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能教训这根没用的肉棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.56,0:32:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有变硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.17,0:32:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.20,0:32:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.51,0:32:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等、等等！不行啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.36,0:33:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.23,0:33:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你说不行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.04,0:33:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我、我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.84,0:33:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.51,0:33:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我衣服都弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.76,0:33:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快迟到了！快让开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.50,0:33:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出门了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.27,0:33:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回来在惩罚你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.91,0:33:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.49,0:34:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁欲生活过了一个月左右、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:09.11,0:35:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.06,0:35:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过来一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.29,0:35:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.84,0:35:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多感觉一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.88,0:35:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.78,0:35:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.29,0:35:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.39,0:35:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.33,0:35:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道做这种事 你会怎么样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.93,0:36:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你说过不准自慰的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.40,0:36:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，，，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.64,0:36:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要偷偷自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.47,0:36:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我、我忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.74,0:36:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.31,0:36:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么还要自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.05,0:36:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行、不行、不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:23.82,0:36:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.56,0:36:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.16,0:36:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要给你惩罚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.17,0:36:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.31,0:36:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.31,0:36:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点肿起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.58,0:36:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是你自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.29,0:37:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样摸会更痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:01.29,0:37:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.99,0:37:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋蛋快受不了了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.36,0:37:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然变得这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.93,0:37:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.87,0:37:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你让它动的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.61,0:37:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为影片太色了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.48,0:37:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是你自己弄得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.55,0:37:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.15,0:37:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得更硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.48,0:37:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会变得更硬吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.52,0:37:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.46,0:37:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手、请你住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.86,0:37:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.53,0:37:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:47.00,0:37:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让它变小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.07,0:37:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒很痛苦的样子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.24,0:37:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:53.28,0:37:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:55.01,0:37:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.08,0:37:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.35,0:38:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.36,0:38:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你偷偷做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.36,0:38:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然就得接受惩罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.56,0:38:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我拆下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.10,0:38:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.15,0:38:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就没办法动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.29,0:38:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.26,0:38:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个样子很适合你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.90,0:38:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.73,0:38:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗？很痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.24,0:38:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.78,0:39:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，再给你更多惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.45,0:39:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你要勃起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.25,0:39:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.15,0:39:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要爆炸了吗？要爆炸了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.26,0:39:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.36,0:39:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.75,0:39:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想被我这样做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.96,0:39:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.89,0:39:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.30,0:39:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.47,0:40:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.45,0:40:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.48,0:40:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:12.32,0:40:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，今天要狠狠地惩罚你才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.56,0:40:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.89,0:40:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.03,0:40:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你绝对不准射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.86,0:40:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.82,0:40:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拆下来楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.41,0:41:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在呼吸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.44,0:41:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.08,0:41:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.35,0:41:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒可以尽情的解放开来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.72,0:41:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来的角度应该是这样才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.46,0:41:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在听吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.60,0:41:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准射精哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.57,0:41:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢射精的话就一年不准你射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.98,0:41:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.06,0:42:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿道都张开了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.09,0:42:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢射精的话十年不准你射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.86,0:42:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才一个月而已 应该很简单吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.71,0:42:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害，都站起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.31,0:42:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都还没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.09,0:42:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍了一个月就变这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.20,0:42:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么变红了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.01,0:42:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和说好的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.58,0:42:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让它变小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.18,0:43:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我、我没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.65,0:43:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.49,0:43:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:07.49,0:43:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.30,0:43:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让你这跟硬邦邦直挺挺的肉棒变小吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.45,0:43:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点变小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.42,0:43:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.16,0:43:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.19,0:43:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变小、变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.70,0:43:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.73,0:43:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.07,0:43:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:58.88,0:44:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.65,0:44:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.49,0:44:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒怎么亮亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.22,0:44:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要变小哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.13,0:44:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我连厕所都不让你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.96,0:44:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:24.40,0:44:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要帮我做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.87,0:44:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没帮你做是让你变小而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.21,0:44:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是肉棒变红的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.75,0:44:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你还是不懂的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.22,0:44:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:49.46,0:44:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.66,0:44:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不行由我决定才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.89,0:45:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.11,0:46:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.82,0:46:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了吗
