Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:26.36,0:46:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是在帮你变小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.70,0:46:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快变小
