Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.12,0:48:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在可是在处罚你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:08.06,0:48:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:10.36,0:48:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这个的话我会更、、、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:30.28,0:48:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得清楚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:35.55,0:48:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是很想看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.36,0:48:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变更硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.67,0:48:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再多处罚你一点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.14,0:49:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.05,0:49:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在期待这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:14.02,0:49:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天一直盯着这里看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:18.73,0:49:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还偷闻我胸罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:24.90,0:49:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想这样做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.38,0:50:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:17.52,0:50:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以射精哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:28.93,0:50:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是处罚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.10,0:50:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让你硬邦邦的肉棒变小才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:39.18,0:50:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:41.41,0:50:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行也得行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:43.28,0:50:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是给你的处罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:49.32,0:50:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要变小才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.22,0:50:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.50,0:51:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.57,0:51:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要更多处罚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.88,0:51:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.92,0:51:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自慰套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.49,0:51:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟肉穴一样吧
