Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:39.56,0:52:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要射时我会停下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.30,0:52:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住了吗
