Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:01.32,0:53:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆出这种变态姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.13,0:53:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小狗一样伸出舌头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.33,0:53:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变小、变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.95,0:53:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:34.55,0:53:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:37.82,0:53:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋蛋也一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.93,0:53:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.86,0:53:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.00,0:53:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要给你更多处罚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.24,0:54:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脚放下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.24,0:54:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.98,0:54:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我说几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.79,0:55:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这肉棒在开心什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.79,0:55:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有你在享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:35.74,0:55:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不是处罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.11,0:55:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根肉棒很想要我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:47.18,0:55:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要被肉穴吸进来一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:58.03,0:56:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是让你开心的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.57,0:56:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是让你变硬
