Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.05,0:56:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不是处罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.65,0:56:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在就反过来 让它变得更硬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:05.30,0:57:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让它变得更硬哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:11.60,0:57:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不准射哦
