Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:45.10,1:42:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样，就让你进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:53.77,1:42:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想插进来吗？ 想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:57.98,1:43:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想插哪里？
