Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:46.53,1:47:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:57.14,1:47:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多做一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.42,1:48:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面进来
